    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为了生存而建造</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭建脚手架、铺设管道并安装照明，提升你的生存几率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/41ac2f239c47b3a7b589a234e465bac4.poster.avif?t=1750651282\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/41ac2f239c47b3a7b589a234e465bac4.webm?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/41ac2f239c47b3a7b589a234e465bac4.mp4?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>对症下药，选对工具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种装备勇闯深渊，但要小心，它们可能也会带来危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/ee23fe58124c803d6d89d221021756d8.poster.avif?t=1750651282\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/ee23fe58124c803d6d89d221021756d8.webm?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/ee23fe58124c803d6d89d221021756d8.mp4?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>交易获取补给</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持良好声誉，才能购买挖掘所需的工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/2e0374d406fd037eaaebc3c8f6de9afc.avif?t=1750651282\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>死亡时，时间仍在流逝</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《最后的挖掘》中没有检查点，只有多年后发现你尸体的新探险者。你能在地球永远封闭前找到宝藏吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/58cae3db38b2d637f365462258831a23.poster.avif?t=1750651282\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/58cae3db38b2d637f365462258831a23.webm?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/58cae3db38b2d637f365462258831a23.mp4?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>获取涂装奖励</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更换你的外观涂装，展现个性风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/c5a5d040877d99ec784de4b72c1a38d6.poster.avif?t=1750651282\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/c5a5d040877d99ec784de4b72c1a38d6.webm?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/c5a5d040877d99ec784de4b72c1a38d6.mp4?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>来自深处的财富</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要敢于挖掘，丰厚奖励就在前方。越往下，回报越大，但风险也越高。地底可能隐藏着一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/6bdf26b93374e58a5c6fb88f99d648c1.poster.avif?t=1750651282\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/6bdf26b93374e58a5c6fb88f99d648c1.webm?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205800/extras/6bdf26b93374e58a5c6fb88f99d648c1.mp4?t=1750651282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
